### Get all posts
GET http://localhost:3000/danubia_api/post

### Create post
POST http://localhost:3000/danubia_api/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Example Post",
    "content": "This is an example post content.",
    "fbPostLink": "https://facebook.com/example",
    "igPostLink": "https://instagram.com/example"
}

